original_title: ONE Friday Fights 3: Chorfah vs. Petsukumvit
overview: ONE Friday Fights: Chorfah vs. Petsukumvit (also known as ONE Lumpinee 3) was a combat sport event produced by ONE Championship that took place on February 3, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand.
title: ONE Friday Fights 3: Chorfah vs. Petsukumvit
